      </div>
      <div class="one-half column category feature_phone_img phones">
        <%= image_tag("phone_screen9.png", class: "u-max-full-width phones") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h1 class = "up_arrow scrollup up_arrow_position3"><a>&#10095</a></h1>
  </div>

<!-- FAQ
–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––– -->
  <article class="faq_scroll">
    <h3 class="section-heading faq_general">FAQ</h3>
  </article>

  <div class="row">
    <ul class="accordion twelve columns" data-accordion role="tablist">
      <li class="accordion-item">
        <!-- The tab title needs role="tab", an href, a unique ID, and aria-controls. -->
        <a href="#panel1d" role="tab" class="accordion-title" id="panel1d-heading" aria-controls="panel1d">How many questions will I receive?</a>
        <p id="panel1d" class="accordion-content" role="tabpanel" data-tab-content aria-labelledby="panel1d-heading">
          Five questions per day.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="accordion-item">
        <a href="#panel1d" role="tab" class="accordion-title" id="panel1d-heading" aria-controls="panel1d">Will I be able to receive questions for any subject available on Text Prep?</a>
        <p id="panel1d" class="accordion-content" role="tabpanel" data-tab-content aria-labelledby="panel1d-heading">
          Yes!!! We want your learning to be as easy as knowing your interests. To receive questions for any subject, simply select the subject you want when logged into your account.  
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="accordion-item">
        <a href="#panel1d" role="tab" class="accordion-title" id="panel1d-heading" aria-controls="panel1d">Can I select more than one subject?</a>
        <p id="panel1d" class="accordion-content" role="tabpanel" data-tab-content aria-labelledby="panel1d-heading">
          You can only select one subject at a time, but you have the freedom to switch subjects at any time.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="accordion-item">
        <a href="#panel1d" role="tab" class="accordion-title" id="panel1d-heading" aria-controls="panel1d">What time will I receive my questions?</a>
        <p id="panel1d" class="accordion-content" role="tabpanel" data-tab-content aria-labelledby="panel1d-heading">
          One question at a time will be sent around 12PM, 2PM, 4PM, 6PM and 8PM (EST) for a total of five questions per day.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="accordion-item">
        <a href="#panel1d" role="tab" class="accordion-title" id="panel1d-heading" aria-controls="panel1d">What happens if I don't answer a question before another gets sent to me?</a>
        <p id="panel1d" class="accordion-content" role="tabpanel" data-tab-content aria-labelledby="panel1d-heading">
          We can only track your answer for your latest question. Stay active and you will stay sharp!
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="accordion-item">
        <a href="#panel1d" role="tab" class="accordion-title" id="panel1d-heading" aria-controls="panel1d">Can I review questions sent to me online?</a>
        <p id="panel1d" class="accordion-content" role="tabpanel" data-tab-content aria-labelledby="panel1d-heading">
          Yes! Your dashboard has a history of questions sent to you, along with your answers and explanations. 
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="accordion-item">
        <a href="#panel1d" role="tab" class="accordion-title" id="panel1d-heading" aria-controls="panel1d">Can I stop receiving questions for a day or two?</a>
        <p id="panel1d" class="accordion-content" role="tabpanel" data-tab-content aria-labelledby="panel1d-heading">
          Yes, of course. When you are logged in you can head on over to the subjects page and deactivate your active subject. When you are ready to begin receiving questions again, simply activate the subject again.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="accordion-item">
        <a href="#panel1d" role="tab" class="accordion-title" id="panel1d-heading" aria-controls="panel1d">Will you offer more subjects?</a>
        <p id="panel1d" class="accordion-content" role="tabpanel" data-tab-content aria-labelledby="panel1d-heading">
          We are always working on updating our current questions and adding more subjects to offer.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="accordion-item">
        <a href="#panel1d" role="tab" class="accordion-title" id="panel1d-heading" aria-controls="panel1d">I have a big exam I am studying for. Can you add it to the list of subjects offered?</a>
        <p id="panel1d" class="accordion-content" role="tabpanel" data-tab-content aria-labelledby="panel1d-heading">
          Glad to hear you would like to use Text Prep to help you study for your exam! Depending on the scope of the material, we could consider adding your subject for all members. Send us an email (<a href="mailto:support@textprep.co" style="border: none; text-transform: lowercase;">support@textprep.co</a>) with your request. 
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

